# Optimize structure with constraints using M06L functional with basis set def2-TZVP and tight SCF settings
! COPT M06L def2-TZVP TightSCF

# Do a frequency calculation (and produce hessian in .hess file)
! AnFreq

# Specify numnber of processors
%pal nprocs 16
     end

# Constrain Calpha atoms
%geom Constraints
        {C [CA_ATOM] C}  # Freeze all coordinates (X, Y, Z) of atom [CA_ATOM]
        end
      end

# Use xyz file as input, first number is the charge of the system, and the second number is the multiplicity (2S+1).
*xyzfile [CHARGE] [MULTIPLICITY] [ID_DIR]/[PDB_ID]_clean.xyz
